<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.237994>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 18. Melittia ambo sp. nov.: 11) ♂ holotype, upperside. Sesiidae picture № 0105 – 2014. Alar expanse 32.5 mm; 12) ditto underside. Sesiidae picture № 0106 – 2014; 13) ♂ paratype, upperside. Sesiidae picture № 0113 – 2014. Alar expanse xx. 5 mm; 14) ditto underside. Sesiidae picture № 0114 – 2014; 15) ♀ paratype, upperside. Sesiidae picture № 0107 – 2014. Alar expanse 34.0 mm; 16) ditto underside. Sesiidae picture № 0108 – 2014. 17) ♀ paratype, upperside. Sesiidae picture № 0109 – 2014. Alar expanse 33.0 mm; 18) ditto underside. Sesiidae picture № 0110 – 2014." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/237994/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.237995>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 – 21. 19) Melittia pyropis Hampson, 1919 male genitalia. Genital preparation № OG – 007 - 2014. Scale bar: 0.5 mm. 20) Melittia ambo sp. nov. male genitalia (paratype). Genital preparation № OG – 006 - 2014. Scale bar: 0.5 mm; 21) Melittia ambo sp. nov. female genitalia (paratype). Genital preparation № OG – 009 - 2014. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/237995/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.237997>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 26. 23) Citrullus colocynthis (L.) Schrad. (Cucurbitaceae), a host plant of M. ambo sp. nov.; 24) root collar of the host plant with a gall formed by a group of larvae; 25) cocoons of M. ambo sp. nov.; 26) freshly emerged female of M. ambo sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/237997/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.237996>
    dc:description "FIGURE 22. Habitat of M. ambo sp. nov. Ethiopia, West Shewa, 3 km S Ambo, 2200 m a. s. l." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/237996/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

